  "texts": [
    "To examine to what extent ChatGPT's responses are consistent in terms of different experiments, the prompt was repeated ten times for each country and each ChatGPT version.",
    "In total, 4,018 topics were created by both ChatGPT versions.",
    "To process these data effectively, we used OpenAI's ChatGPT application programming interface (API) 43; see Supplementary Note 2.",
    "Following an approach by Kim et al.",
    "16, we instructed the system to act as a helpful assistant and then began using our prompt."
  ],
